      "text": "Flying Saucers Exist?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Californian, Who 'Talks' to Men",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "From the Stars, Says 'Yes';",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Scientists Assail Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "By ELLIOT CARLSON",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Staff Reporter of THE WALL STREET JOURNAL",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "They're back. The latest was sighted a few",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "nights ago by residents and pilots in the north-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "ern tier of states and Canada. They described",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "it as an orange fireball. The Air Force at first",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "called it an unidentified flying object, but now",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "thinks it was a meteor. Some other people",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "called it a flying saucer.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Several people say they saw the fireball land",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Saturday night. An 11-year-old boy in Lorain,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Ohio, says he watched it drop into the woods",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "near his home. A woman in Elyria, Ohio, 10",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "miles away, claims she saw it plunge into a",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "vacant lot across the street from her home.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Others say they saw it streak into Lake Michi-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "gan. Scientists and police combed a 75-acre",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "area near Pittsburgh after a woman there saw",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "an object crash to earth \"smoldering.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Despite these witnesses and search efforts,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "however, the thing has yet to be found. In this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "regard, it is like all other unidentified flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "objects, or UFOs, which are mysterious be-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "cause they are seen but never found.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Whatever it turns out to be-meteor, sniglet,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "part, hoax, weather oddity or man from",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Mars-it appeared in a banner year for such",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "objects, which almost disappeared from public",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "consciousness following a rash of reports of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "flying saucers in the mid-1950s: \"We've had",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "more reports this year than in any year since",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "1957, when we had more than a thousand,\" says",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "a spokesman for Project Blue Book, the Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "Force program set up in 1948 to evaluate re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "ports of the phenomena.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "Men From Outer Space",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "Nobody knows what the objects are or where",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "they come from, but there is no lack of theories",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "or of controversy. The Amalgamated Flying",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "Saucer Clubs of America, Inc., is sure the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "\"saucers\" come from outer space. How do",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "they know? The \"space people\" have told",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "Not only that, says Gabriel Green, who",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "heads the California group, \"space people give",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "us advance information about life on other",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "planets and solutions to insurmountable prob-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "lems on our planet.\" One suggestion allegedly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "made to Mr. Green in 1960 by a visit from Al-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "pha Centauri, a nearby star: Run for Presi-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "dent as a write-in candidate. (He campaigned",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "briefly, then decided not to run.)",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "The National Investigations Committee on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "Aerial Phenomena (NICAP), a private re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "search organization in Washington, doesn't",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "agree with that theory. \"We reject reports of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "people beings landing on earth to solve all our",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "problems,\" says a spokesman. So men from",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "Mars are a lot of bunk? Not necessarily, says",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "the committee. It believes a Congressional in-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "vestigation would prove that UFOs \"are real",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "physical objects . . . under the control of living",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "beings.\" As an afterthought, the spokesman",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "adds: \"There are a tremendous number of ego-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "maniacs who have been able to appoint them-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "selves experts in this field because it's so eso-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "teric.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "One man who's not confused at all is Charles",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "A. Lamey, professor emeritus of physics and",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "mathematics at Defiance College in Ohio. Says",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
