      "text": "with magnetic fields.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "'There's Nothing To It\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "Such notions are scoffed at by astronomers,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "however. \"All this is imagination outside the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "realm of science,\" says Donald H. Menzel, di-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "rector of the observatory at Harvard. \"I have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "examined Air Force cases and discovered that",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "they all have simple explanations in terms",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "of well-known natural phenomena. There's not",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "one cause, but hundreds. Some are quite spec-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "tacular, such as reflections from ice crystals or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "bright stars, searchlights on clouds or high-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "flying spider webs. But to some people the exis-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "tence of flying saucers is a matter of religious",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "conviction,\" he says.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "But Mr. Menzel reads more into the Air",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "Force data than does the Air Force itself. Of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "the 9,700 UFO reports made to the Air Force",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "since 1947, 673 remain classified as \"unidenti-",
