      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "text": "they received nor discovered any evidence that",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "proves the existence of intraspace mobility or",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "text": "extraterrestrial life and we continue to extend",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "text": "an open invitation to anyone who feels he pos-",
