    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 138,
      "text": "the Air Force, is that the matter should be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 139,
      "text": "studied more thoroughly.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 140,
      "text": "\"Pressures to conformity in academic cir-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141,
      "text": "cles and fear of ridicule have slowed the",
      "status": "image_matched"
