    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 149,
      "text": "risk of being unpopular, Mr. Salisbury told the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 150,
      "text": "fifth annual Space Conference this year that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 151,
      "text": "\"there may be some natural explanation of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 152,
      "text": "these things, but a tentative possibility to be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 153,
      "text": "considered is that UFOs are spaceships from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 154,
      "text": "Mars.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155,
      "text": "Fueling the flying-saucer controversy has",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 156,
      "text": "been the large number of reports from what",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 157,
      "text": "many people consider reliable witnesses-pilots",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 158,
      "text": "with technical backgrounds. Since 1947, more",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 159,
      "text": "than 100 private, military and commercial pilots",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 160,
      "text": "have reported spotting strange objects in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 161,
      "text": "sky, according to one study.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 162,
      "text": "Pinning down such reports is difficult, how-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 163,
      "text": "ever. \"Some of the boys did report things they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
